Season chicken, if desired, with salt and pepper. Heat oil in 12-inch nonstick skillet over medium-high heat and cook chicken, stirring occasionally, 5 minutes or until chicken is thoroughly cooked. Remove chicken and set aside. Stir water, peanut butter, vinegar and ginger into same skillet. Bring to a boil over high heat. Stir in Knorr(R) Sides Plus(TM) Veggies - Vegetable Fried Rice. Cover and cook over medium heat, stirring occasionally, 8 minutes or until rice is tender. Stir in chicken and green onions; heat through. Serve, if desired, with finely chopped fresh cilantro, fresh lime wedges and chopped peanuts.